[[module css]]
@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Special+Elite');

.manifestoPaper {
    color: #351f11;
    font-family: Courier;
    font-size: 14px;
    background: url('http://www.rpc-wiki.net/local--files/malthusian-manifesto/PaperTexture.jpg');
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    background-size: cover;
    box-shadow: 4px 6px #dbdbd9;
    padding: 10px;
    font-family: 'Special Elite', cursive;
}
[[/module]]
[[include :scp-wiki-cn:credit:start]]


[[include :scp-wiki-cn:credit:end]]

[[div class="manifestoPaper"]]

= **[[size large]]别楚剑客[[/size]]**

= **（佚名）**

**丁卯年末，左迁平襄，遇异胡[[footnote]]异胡：与下文的“狄胡”、“异种”意同，均指狄瓦族。[[/footnote]]残兵，左右皆死。幸得楚地剑客襄助，斩杀四十余骑。相谈甚欢，作此篇纪[[footnote]]纪：通记。[[/footnote]]之。**



= **[[size large]]楚客引龙泉，紫电破残垣。[[/size]]**

= **[[size large]]挥剑裂赤甲，恶血映长天。[[/size]]**

= **[[size large]]少意瞩青山，纵马立狂峦。[[/size]]**

= **[[size large]]忽遇白髯公，岿阳一真仙。[[/size]]**

= **[[size large]]从此入道门，萦回二十年。[[/size]]**

= **[[size large]]北海涤发冠，白玉京[[footnote]]白玉京：指天帝所居之处，亦为月亮的别称。[[/footnote]]中眠。[[/size]]**

= **[[size large]]无意染尘氛，乐道松林间。[[/size]]**

= **[[size large]]狄胡起杀戮，凄凄生民怜。[[/size]]**

= **[[size large]]奇巧铄金石，谲计塞河川。[[/size]]**

= **[[size large]]小卒舍身死，将军碧血干。[[/size]]**

= **[[size large]]独入荒蛮地，斩渠[[footnote]]渠：意指渠首。[[/footnote]]镇西边。[[/size]]**

= **[[size large]]三年[[[SCP-140|异种]]]败，瀛洲[[footnote]]瀛洲：古代中国神话传说中的东海仙山。[[/footnote]]终所还。[[/size]]**

[[/div]]
